title: Reward Gen Zero PanckaeSwap Users
body: Allow a non-bot ticketd auction for NFTs (or cake) for ONLY original users. Somehow you will have to combat the mass influx of bots that stopped many of us this morning partaking in the Pancake Squad launch. Many are disappointed. :/
